Class Neo4JPersistor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework.persistance.CoalescePersistorBase
      • com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework.persistance.neo4j.Neo4JPersistor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICoalescePersistor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Neo4jSearchPersister

    public class Neo4JPersistor
extends CoalescePersistorBase
    Neo4j Implementation. Extend and override getGroups(CoalesceEntity) and getClassification(CoalesceEntity) to add security handling.

    n78554
